      <section>
         <p>You must check all measurements and calibrate as needed.
Take extra care to calibrate the transformer and the output current:<ul>
               <li>
                  <p>Transformer output voltage calibration: The characteristics
of the output transformer must be compensated to guarantee the 1%
output accuracy independent of the load.</p>
               </li>
               <li>
                  <p>Output current calibration: For a correct indication of the
load percentage and for the correct detection of an overload situation
and the transformer compensation.</p>
               </li>
            </ul>
         </p>
      </section>
